The easiest way to install the directory client packages on RHEL 7 is with:
# yum groups install "Directory Client"
# yum install pam_krb5
# yum install ipa-client

Red Hat recommends:
# yum install authconfig-gtk sssd krb5-workstation pam_krb5
and if needed for IPA or Windows authentication:
# yum install ipa-client samba-winbind realmd
